CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 18, 1962, pg. 1 reads: "All-Night Gospel Sing For Drafts Fund-The Murrell Singers, popular group of Pittsburgh singers, are shown sending the message to the large crowd."
TitMainTitle: The Murrell Singers, including woman wearing geometric patterned dress and hoop earrings, singing into microphone, in Calvary Baptist Church for All Night Gospel Sing for the Charles "Buggsy" Drafts Fund
